  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nilsen, ?] this lawyer, what he had seen, even though he was not supposed to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Franz [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nilsen ?] came to the conclusion that any country where this could happen, he didn't want to live in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father convinced him that he was pushing it a little bit too far and that he shouldn't.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when we ultimately were on our way to Buchenwald, my father said to me, he said, you know, Fritz, you and I are probably the only ones who know what we can look forward to if it is true what [?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nilsen ?] told us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] my mother asked the-- those three gentlemen-- 'gentlemen' in quotation marks-- if she could fix breakfast for us, so that we wouldn't leave on an empty stomach.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, by the time breakfast time comes around, they will be home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they forgot to tell her which day or month we would come home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And our car was parked in front of our house and was a new car.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, in order to get us home faster, we should take our car.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was naive enough to sit behind the wheel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, get in the back of the car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I drive the car, one of the SS men said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was the last time we saw the car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went to Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on the way, as we got closer to Gestapo headquarters-- it was still dark-- we saw, like, ghosts, people, other people, friends of ours, on their way to Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And among them was a quite famous physician, who was a very famous ear, nose, and throat specialist, [GERMAN] Dr.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
